modules.description: This module generates functions to spatially transform user-defined abstract and record types that include transformable types like `Scad_ml.Scad.t` and `Scad_ml.Vec3.t`. It supports operations such as `translate`, `scale`, `rotate`, `mirror`, and transformations around specific points or with quaternions, applying them selectively based on field annotations like `[@scad.unit]`, `[@scad.ignore]`, and `[@scad.map]`. It is used to manipulate complex geometric data structures while preserving semantic constraints on their components.
